first load these two packages:


\usepackage{booktabs}
\usepackage{caption}

for maths use array:

\[
\begin{array}{ll}
\toprule
f(x)   & f'(x) \\
\midrule
x^n    & nx^{n-1} \\
e^x    & e^x \\
\sin x & \cos x \\
\bottomrule
\end{array}
\]


for text you use tabular

\begin{center}
\begin{tabular}{ll}
\toprule
Alcaloide & Origine \\
\midrule
atropina  & belladonna \\
morfina   & papavero \\
nicotina  & tabacco \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{center}

